{
  "1833680": {
    "name": "元气百响",
    "steam_appid": 1833680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/d2bbb3312ef4b64a4194109883c49e18.avif?t=1737785280\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【故事】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个人类与意识生物“库鲁鲁”共存的世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对库鲁鲁本质与机理的研究，目前仍然没有得出任何达成广泛共识的结论。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但大致可以确定的是：它是一种生命体，与一切人类精神与生理律动共存和共鸣，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能够在人类认知、思考或交流时，与人类互相影响。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类必须与库鲁鲁保持良性的平衡才能确保神智与认知能力的稳定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，只有极少数人类可以视觉识别、物理感知和操控库鲁鲁，并加以系统的研究。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们称之为“调谐师”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个夏天，弥奥依（勉强）通过了职业考试，与卡苏娜、汐丝作为见习调谐师来到了百响城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一座有着近两世纪历史，但与外界交流并不多的沿海城市，近十年却备受调谐师协会关注。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而随着例行任务的遂行，这座大都市开始变得异常，群体失调现象似乎越来越普遍而严重。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与此同时，接获特殊委托的两名神秘调谐师也来到了百响城……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/a77c6a80032a58df3f86aa43cd4497c8.avif?t=1737785280\" width=540 height=764 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【探索】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>· 揭开百响城的秘密</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  从随机的路线收获不同的奇遇，每次成功的巡查都向“真相”走近。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/8f973efad1e8b226f7f953ae91591d73.poster.avif?t=1737785280\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/8f973efad1e8b226f7f953ae91591d73.webm?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/8f973efad1e8b226f7f953ae91591d73.mp4?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/10371a891b400ac304af3290db13f951.poster.avif?t=1737785280\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/10371a891b400ac304af3290db13f951.webm?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/10371a891b400ac304af3290db13f951.mp4?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>· 纸牌式城市巡查</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  翻开危机重重的任务卡牌，小心应对，为你的队伍做出最佳的冒险决策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/6b15ed9a18c80468cbdef83d4ad373ed.avif?t=1737785280\" width=540 height=764 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【战斗】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>· 美少女打铁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  一键打出华丽连招，看准时机进行格挡，只有攻防但变化无穷的快节奏战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/d3ee0e5e697d91810d35718411aa1428.poster.avif?t=1737785280\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/d3ee0e5e697d91810d35718411aa1428.webm?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/d3ee0e5e697d91810d35718411aa1428.mp4?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/a727e45dad39c9c8f1766022d9562767.avif?t=1737785280\" width=540 height=764 /></span></p>",
